parameters: \nw[Fross]This is... without a doubt, the Fruit of Flaurus.

\nw[\N[1]]Really? Then I'll go get it and come back right
away.
I obtained the Fruit of Flaurus.
\nw[Uka]Something... is coming...

\nw[\N[1]]I managed to defeat it somehow... but is this what
danger feels like?
\nw[Uka]It's still... there...
\nw[\N[1]]Huh?
\nw[\N[1]]Three of them!?
\nw[Uka]More... are coming... gathering... coming...

\nw[Huma]Seriously!? It was already tough dealing with just
one, so what are we gonna do if a bunch of them
come?! Dalton, can't your years of experience help
us out somehow?

\nw[Dalton]Hmm... Even if we go back, it's a dead end. We
have no choice but to somehow break through one
point and run through.

\nw[Huma]Seriously, but what should we do if there are
three of them...
\nw[\N[1]]If these things are gathering, we need to hurry...
\nw[Uka]......? Wait... something even more amazing is...
\nw[\N[1]]Huh?

\nw[Uka]As I thought... something different is
approaching...
\nw[\N[1]]......No way... this voice...
\nw[\N[1]]No way... something like that...
\nw[Uka]......What... happened...?
\nw[\N[1]]Eek!
\nw[Uka]......\N[1]... are you okay...?

\nw[\N[1]]No, it's scary... I'm scared... I can't believe...
I'm still... in a place like this...
\nw[Uka]...Are you scared...?

\nw[Fross]......You look pale. I want to examine you
properly, but right now...

\nw[Rodrigo]For now, have \N[1] step back. We'll break through
together.

\nw[Huma]Seriously, if it's for the sake of survival,
there's no choice but to do our best.
\nw[Dalton]Yes, when I give the signal, everyone...
\nw[The One Who Devours]\{\{\{Oooooohhhhhh!!!!\}
\nw[\N[1]]Nooo!
\nw[Huma]Ugh, isn't that giant body an Eater?
\nw[Uka]......Empty?
\nw[Huma]Ah, since we're citizens, maybe we came to help?

\nw[Dalton]That can't be true! I heard something like that
from Prae a long time ago. The <One Who Devours>
doesn't have the ability to distinguish between
friend and foe.

\nw[Dalton]Let's run away immediately! We'll pass through
while they're fighting!
\nw[\N[1]]No... No... Nooo!!
\nw[Fross]\N[1]-chan isn't moving.
\nw[Dalton]Rodrigo, carry me and run!
\nw[Rodrigo]Alright, leave it to me.
\nw[Dalton]Let's go!
back_40_1
\nw[Dalton]How is it? Did you manage to separate them?
\nw[Uka]......Big person......coming this way......

\nw[Dalton]Tch, did they already defeat the monsters? But why
are they chasing after us? There are still other
monsters, right?!

\nw[Uka]......They're defeating the
monsters......but......they're faster than
us......
\nw[Dalton]Damn, even if we run quickly...

\nw[Fross]Haa, haa, haa... I don't have much confidence in
my physical strength.
\nw[Thorz]*panting*... So tired...

\nw[Dalton]The magicians are here, and neither me nor Rodrigo
are particularly fast. \N[1] seems to be trembling
and unable to move...

\nw[Dalton]Should we let Uka, who is the fastest, go ahead
and call for reinforcements?

\nw[Dalton]No, if Uka, who has a high scouting ability, is
gone, we will quickly be surrounded by monsters
and caught up.
\nw[Dalton]A voice...!
\nw[Uka]...Already...close...soon...they'll catch up...

\nw[Dalton]Damn, they're too fast. In this situation, someone
has to stop them.
\nw[Uka]......Uka......will...go...ahead...
\nw[Dalton]Wait! If you're not here, I can't escape...
\nw[The One Who Devours]\{\{\{Oooooohhhhhh!!!!\}
\nw[Uka]......They're here......I'll go......
\nw[Dalton]They're right there! Wait, it can't be you...!
\nw[Dalton]The <One Who Devours>...fell?
\nw[???]Be careful, stay back.

\nw[Dalton]Who are you...? How did you make the <One Who
Devours> fall...?

\nw[Fross]Are you... Miss Fee? I believe you're a friend of
Louis...

\nw[???]Yeah, we meet again. Even if I die at the hands of
a familiar face, I have a bad habit of not waking
up, so lend me a hand.
\nw[???]So, all of you...
\nw[Fross]Be careful, behind you!
\nw[???]Huh?
\nw[Fross]!

\nw[Dalton]Are you destroying the ground where I can stand
and making me fall...?

\nw[???]Can you all run to the entrance of the forest?
Please hurry as much as possible.
\nw[Fross]However, if that's the case, Miss Fee...

\nw[???]I don't really understand the situation, but
you're running away, right? If that's the case, I
want you to go quickly. Because my borrowed weapon
is going to break.
\nw[???]And besides, that child over there is scared too.
\nw[\N[1]]Ugh... I don't want to...
\nw[Fross]Ugh...

\nw[Dalton]I don't really understand what's going on, but
let's go! They said they'll help us. We'll just be
a burden if we stay here.

\nw[Fross]Understood... Thank you very much, Miss Fee!
Please take care!
\nw[???]Yeah, see you later~
\nw[The One Who Devours]\{\{\{Oooooohhhhhh!!!!\}

\nw[Dalton]We ran quite a bit... but I can't hear any sound
anymore.

\nw[Huma]Looks like we managed to escape, huh? Phew, thank
goodness.

\nw[Fross]Haa, haa... Miss Fee, are you okay? I'm really
worried.

\nw[Dalton]From their appearance, they seemed completely at
ease. There's probably no problem.
\nw[Dalton]More importantly, do you know that woman?

\nw[Fross]Um... She is a friend of Louis-san. When I came to
Rimuru, she accompanied me together with Louis-
san...

\nw[Fross]But, I've never seen her fight before. So I don't
know if she's strong or not...

\nw[Huma]Ah~ What I was doing earlier was just breaking the
ground. It's not that difficult to move the earth
using earth magic.

\nw[Thorz]Haa, haa... What are you saying, you amateur in
magic.

\nw[Thorz]Normally, there's no way you can knock someone
down like that with magic. Besides, that giant was
also fast. If it were so easy to deal with him
using earth magic, no one would have struggled.

\nw[Thorz]In the first place, that woman was swinging her
sword and destroying the ground. If she were using
magic, there would be no need to swing a sword
like that. I don't think that woman is a magician.

\nw[Dalton]Close combat fighters become weaker if the footing
is bad. This is a basic principle and it applies
to <predators> as well.
\nw[Dalton]But, to be able to do it so easily...

\nw[Fross]Uka-chan? You haven't seemed energetic since
earlier, were you scared after all?
\nw[Uka]......No......I don't know......

\nw[Uka]......I don't know......It's my first time......My
body is......trembling......

\nw[Fross]Don't worry, you're safe now. Uka-chan, you don't
have to worry, okay? That big guy won't come back
anymore, you know?
\nw[Uka]......Big guy...?

\nw[Uka]......No......That person might not be thinking
anything......
\nw[Fross]Eh, is that so? In that case, why...
\nw[Uka]......That woman...she was really...strange...
\nw[Fross]Strange?

\nw[Uka]......I didn't notice...until it was right in
front of me...

\nw[Uka]......Even though it was right in front of me... I
couldn't tell... I could see it... and hear its
voice...
\nw[Uka]......That's all......There's nothing else......
\nw[Fross]......

\nw[Fross]It's okay. That just means you're feeling scared.
It's normal to be afraid of things you don't
understand.
\nw[Fross]Look, please hold my hand.
\nw[Fross]You're a good girl. How about it, isn't it warm?

\nw[Fross]Doesn't the trembling lessen a little when it's
warm?
\nw[Fross]Yes, then let's hold hands and go outside.
\nw[Uka]......Yeah......I understand......

\nw[Fross]Hehe, you can also get closer physically, you
know.

\nw[Dalton]It's about time we're outside the forest. Phew...
Well, I'm glad things worked out somehow...
\nw[\N[1]]Like that...

fruit by fully recovering. Will you go back?
